ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f6ffc6298ccbd7ba823c43562787afd57e9209b","tid":2304542,"uid":159307,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"睇英文片<br />\n初期開英文字幕<br />\n後期可以試試熄埋佢<br />\n<br />\n蝗語呢啲垃圾就算把啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:09:18.000Z","msg":"建議樓主買個netflix"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"Netflix The Crown or The Queen&lsquo;s Gambit are good enough for learning <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:19:20.000Z","msg":"睇多啲都唔怕啦"},{"pid":"37a584e02dbafd858c42810b6f1f893b43ac537a","tid":2304542,"uid":381305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"聽：開字幕睇西片，再閂字幕睇一次，當功課咁做。開始進步就掉轉，睇無字幕先。<br />\n講：聽得多自然想講，溝件abc鬼妹日日9吹。溝唔到，自己打飛機對鏡頭講，讀報紙。<br />\n讀：9睇英文，手機atm乜7都轉英文版。<br />\n寫：grammar要上堂學才會快，上堂練習做句，比老師批改，再日日自己9寫日記<br />\n個人：學語文要愛上當地文化。好似愛上日本av文化一樣，接觸得多，自然識幾句日文，進步神速。學文化等於學slang和粗口，係學語文的最後一步"},{"pid":"54cedd4ffd255c6703e276128df5719a41a0b317","tid":2304542,"uid":342086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab0390b90e7f62934537475f410855b21e5b7952","tid":2304542,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"我今年43歲，準備緊移民英國但語文能力不足（廠長level），有無方法可以使自己語文能力半年內進步很多？<br />\n<br />\n為了答謝大家，送上雞排妹J圖兩張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKrP6T6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKrP6T6.jpg&h=73de79fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjjKbkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjjKbkN.jpg&h=0c9e420d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"1. 買本Grammar 書睇 <br />\n2. 睇多d youtube (talk show: Jimmy Fallon/Jimmy Kimmel)<br />\n3. 睇戲（可以全中文字幕睇一次先， 明白晒套戲講咩再全英文字幕or 冇字幕齋聽， 自己模仿下角色d 對白）非常有用<br />\n4. 聽 Podcast (Spotify/ Iphone 內置podcast app etc 都可以download 到）， 番工搭車個陣唔聽歌可以聽呢d 節目<br />\n5. ching有冇咩興趣同英文可以扯上關係， 例如睇波既，英超/NBA咪上網睇d 足球籃球節目， 球員訪問<br />\n<br />\n平時好小聽同講要你即刻用英文溝通就會好緊張，最緊要係keep 住令自己係個英語環境。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ygb4V0s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgb4V0s.png&h=36c03eba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef9a83d987db9a9f71ea0d00ace6a46c6c4481af","tid":2304542,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"睇有劇情嘅英文av"},{"pid":"6189a1f9daced23d9479d1a26cc694737ded0ded","tid":2304542,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37a584e02dbafd858c42810b6f1f893b43ac537a","tid":2304542,"uid":381305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"聽：開字幕睇西片，再閂字幕睇一次，當功課咁做。開始進步就掉轉，睇無字幕先。<br />\n講：聽得多自然想講，溝件abc鬼妹日日9吹。溝唔到，自己打飛機對鏡頭講，讀報紙。<br />\n讀：9睇英文，手機atm乜7都轉英文版。<br />\n寫：grammar要上堂學才會快，上堂練習做句，比老師批改，再日日自己9寫日記<br />\n個人：學語文要愛上當地文化。好似愛上日本av文化一樣，接觸得多，自然識幾句日文，進步神速。學文化等於學slang和粗口，係學語文的最後一步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db670fc31ea414c456d76f0bf521391833baf60a","tid":2304542,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54cedd4ffd255c6703e276128df5719a41a0b317","tid":2304542,"uid":342086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab0390b90e7f62934537475f410855b21e5b7952","tid":2304542,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"我今年43歲，準備緊移民英國但語文能力不足（廠長level），有無方法可以使自己語文能力半年內進步很多？<br />\n<br />\n為了答謝大家，送上雞排妹J圖兩張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKrP6T6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKrP6T6.jpg&h=73de79fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjjKbkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjjKbkN